<h2 class="red-text">Philosopher Database</h2>

<p style="text-align:center;">
  
  <img class="larger-image thick-green-border" src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/94/Sanzio_01.jpg"></p>


<p>
From the founder of western philosophy, Socrates, to philosophers of the present day. This database will list their main ideas, characteristics, and their degree of influences and comparisons to each other.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Let us begin with the one who is considered to have had a profound effect on philosophy. Presenting the one who never wrote anything! You know who it is already, the one and only Socrates! 
